# UI Philosophy

- The TUI is keyboard-first and audit-first.
- Preserve fast navigation and terminal-native workflows.
- Do not hide reasoning behind polished visuals.
- Audit surfaces are first-class, not secondary dialogs.
- UI work must not force compromises in kernel correctness.
